      prompt: `<div style='text-align:center'><em>y</em> = <em>x</em> + 19<br><em>y</em> = −<em>x</em> + 33</div>The solution to the given system of equations is (<em>x</em>, <em>y</em>). What is the value of 2<em>y</em>?`,
