      prompt: `To cut a lawn, Antwan charges a fee of $15.00 for his equipment and $8.50 per hour spent cutting a lawn. Taylor charges a fee of $12.00 for her equipment and $9.00 per hour spent cutting a lawn. If <em>x</em> represents the number of hours spent cutting a lawn, what are all the values of <em>x</em> for which Taylor’s total charge is greater than Antwan’s total charge?`,
